public class StudySubjectHandler
extends java.lang.Object
implements javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPHandler<javax.xml.ws.handler.soap.SOAPMessageContext>

This handler restructures the buggy isSubjectResponse from OC 3.1.2. See issue report 13411 (https://issuetracker.openclinica.com/view.php?id=13411).

Author:
Arjan van der Velde (ag.vandervelde@vumc.nl)
